 Manual Heat Press Machine For Garment Features:

 Introducing our state-of-the-art 38x38cm Specialty Swing-away & Pull-out Drawer Manual Heat Press Machine for Garments, a must-have for any printing enthusiast or professional crafter. Engineered with precision and versatility, this heat press is designed to elevate your garment decoration endeavors to new heights.
Crafted with a spacious 38x38cm (15×15 inch) heat platen, this machine offers ample surface area for printing various sizes of garments, from tees and hoodies to tote bags and more. The swing-away design provides effortless access to the heating element, ensuring precise positioning of your materials and minimizing the risk of accidental burns.
But what truly sets this heat press apart is its innovative pull-out drawer feature. Say goodbye to awkward maneuvering and struggling to align your designs perfectly. With the pull-out drawer, you can effortlessly slide your garment onto the platen, allowing for seamless placement and accurate printing every time.
Suitable for a wide range of applications, this heat press is perfect for creating custom t-shirts, jerseys, hats, and other apparel items. Whether you’re a seasoned professional or just starting out, you’ll appreciate the intuitive controls and user-friendly interface, making it easy to achieve professional-quality results with every press.
Constructed from durable materials and built to last, this heat press is designed to withstand the rigors of daily use. Plus, its compact footprint makes it ideal for home studios, craft rooms, or small businesses with limited space.
Elevate your garment printing game with the 38x38cm Specialty Swing-away & Pull-out Drawer Manual Heat Press Machine for Garments. Unlock your creativity and bring your designs to life with precision, efficiency, and style.

details:

  4R Resin Coated Photo Paper 100 Sheets 260g quantity

Description
Introducing our premium 4R Resin Coated Photo Paper, the perfect choice for capturing and preserving your most cherished memories! With 100 sheets of high-quality, 260gsm photo paper in each pack, you can bring your photos to life with stunning clarity and detail.
Crafted with a resin-coated surface, our photo paper delivers professional-grade results that rival those of traditional photo labs. The glossy finish enhances color vibrancy and sharpness, ensuring that your photos make a lasting impression every time.
Suitable for a wide range of uses, including:
Photography Printing: Produce gallery-worthy prints of your favorite photos with rich, true-to-life colors and exceptional detail.
Home Photo Albums: Create beautiful photo albums to showcase your family vacations, milestones, and special moments.
Professional Portfolios: Impress clients and colleagues with high-quality prints for your photography portfolio or business presentations.
Scrapbooking: Preserve memories and create visually stunning scrapbook layouts with durable, archival-quality photo prints.
DIY Projects: Get creative with arts and crafts projects, including greeting cards, collages, and wall art featuring your own photos.
Thanks to its heavyweight construction and quick-drying surface, our resin-coated photo paper is ideal for both amateur photographers and professionals alike. Plus, with its standard 4R size (4 x 6 inches), it’s compatible with most photo printers, making it convenient to use for all your printing needs.
Experience the difference that premium-quality photo paper can make and turn your memories into tangible works of art with our 4R Resin Coated Photo Paper. Whether you’re printing snapshots for your personal collection or creating professional-grade prints for your business, our photo paper delivers exceptional results that you’ll be proud to display and share.

Description
Introducing our A4 Resin Coated Photo Paper – the go-to choice for professional-quality prints that stand the test of time. With 20 sheets of heavyweight, 260gsm photo paper in each pack, you’ll achieve stunning results with every print.
Crafted with a resin-coated surface, our photo paper delivers exceptional color reproduction, sharpness, and durability. The glossy finish enhances the vibrancy of your photos, making them pop with lifelike detail.
Perfect for a variety of uses, including:
Photography Printing: Produce gallery-worthy prints of your favorite photos with rich, true-to-life colors and impeccable detail.
Professional Portfolios: Impress clients and colleagues with high-quality prints for your photography portfolio, business presentations, or exhibitions.
Home Décor: Create striking wall art, photo albums, or framed prints to adorn your living space with cherished memories.
Scrapbooking: Preserve special moments and create visually stunning scrapbook layouts with durable, archival-quality photo prints.
Gifts and Keepsakes: Make personalized gifts for friends and family by printing cherished photos onto cards, calendars, or other keepsake items.
Thanks to its heavyweight construction and quick-drying surface, our resin-coated photo paper is ideal for both amateur photographers and professionals alike. Plus, with its A4 size, it’s compatible with most photo printers, making it convenient to use for all your printing needs.
Experience the difference that premium-quality photo paper can make and turn your memories into tangible works of art with our A4 Resin Coated Photo Paper. Whether you’re printing snapshots for your personal collection or showcasing your professional work, our photo paper ensures exceptional results that you’ll be proud to display and share.

Instruction:

Wait for a few minutes, and gently remove the paper.
The design should be on your skin.
Introducing our A4 Tattoo Paper – your gateway to temporary body art that’s as expressive as it is versatile. With 3 sheets of premium-quality tattoo paper in each pack, you can unleash your creativity and adorn yourself with stunning designs.
Crafted for convenience and safety, our tattoo paper is easy to use and gentle on the skin. Simply print your desired design onto the special transfer paper using an inkjet printer, apply the adhesive sheet, and transfer the tattoo to your skin with water. Voila! You have a temporary tattoo that looks vibrant and feels comfortable.
Perfect for:
Personal Expression: Showcase your individuality with custom tattoos that reflect your personality, mood, or style.
Special Occasions: Add an extra element of fun to parties, festivals, or events with themed temporary tattoos for guests of all ages.
Cosplay and Costuming: Bring your favorite characters to life with temporary tattoos that complete your cosplay ensemble.
Trial Runs: Experiment with tattoo designs before committing to permanent ink, ensuring you love the look before making a lifelong commitment.
Promotional Purposes: Promote your brand, business, or event with custom temporary tattoos that serve as unique and memorable giveaways.
With its A4 size, our tattoo paper provides ample space for large, intricate designs or multiple smaller tattoos on a single sheet. Plus, the tattoos are easy to remove with soap and water, allowing you to change up your look as often as you like.
Embrace your artistic side and make a statement with our A4 Tattoo Paper – the perfect blend of creativity, convenience, and temporary flair. Whether you’re expressing yourself, celebrating an occasion, or exploring new looks, our tattoo paper is your canvas for self-expression.

Description
Introducing our A4 Cold Laminate Film – the perfect solution for protecting and enhancing your prints with ease! Each pack contains 20 sheets of high-quality laminate film, offering durability and a glossy finish for your projects.
Designed for simplicity and versatility, our cold laminate film is easy to apply without the need for heat or special equipment. Simply peel off the backing and apply the film to your prints for a protective layer that resists moisture, scratches, and fading.
Suitable for a variety of uses, including:
Document Protection: Preserve important documents, certificates, and photos with a durable laminate coating that extends their lifespan.
Signage and Displays: Create professional-looking signs, posters, and displays for events, exhibitions, and presentations, adding a glossy finish that enhances colors and graphics.
Art and Crafts: Seal and protect your artwork, drawings, and DIY projects with a glossy laminate film that adds a polished look and protects against damage.
Educational Materials: Enhance teaching materials, flashcards, and learning aids with a protective laminate coating that withstands frequent handling and extends their usability.
Labeling and Packaging: Add a glossy finish to product labels, packaging inserts, and promotional materials, making your brand stand out and adding a layer of protection to your designs.
Thanks to its A4 size, our cold laminate film is compatible with most standard paper sizes, making it convenient for a wide range of applications. Plus, with its adhesive backing, applying the film is quick and easy – simply trim to size, peel, and stick!
Protect and enhance your prints with our A4 Cold Laminate Film. Whether you’re preserving important documents, creating eye-catching signage, or adding a glossy finish to your crafts, our laminate film is the perfect choice for professional-quality results.

  A4 Matt Photo Paper (Sticker) 50 Sheets quantity

Description
Introducing our A4 Matt Photo Paper (Sticker) – the perfect blend of quality and convenience for all your printing needs! With 50 sheets per pack, this adhesive-backed photo paper offers endless possibilities for creating vibrant, durable prints.
Crafted with a matte finish, our photo paper delivers exceptional color reproduction and sharp detail, ensuring that your photos look their best every time. The adhesive backing makes it easy to turn your prints into stickers, allowing you to decorate scrapbooks, journals, greeting cards, and more with ease.
Ideal for a variety of uses, including:
1. Scrapbooking: Preserve your memories and create stunning layouts with adhesive-backed prints that add dimension to your projects.
2. Crafts and DIY Projects: Add personalized touches to handmade cards, party favors, gift tags, and other creative projects.
3. Home Décor: Decorate your living space with custom wall art, photo collages, and decorative accents made from your favorite photos.
4. Organizational Tools: Stay organized with custom labels, tags, and stickers for home or office use.
5. Personalized Gifts: Make thoughtful gifts for friends and family by turning your photos into stickers for notebooks, laptops, and more.
With its A4 size, our photo paper is compatible with most inkjet printers, making it easy to print your designs at home. Plus, the adhesive backing ensures that your prints stay in place once applied, so you can enjoy your creations for years to come.
Transform your photos into stickers and bring your creative visions to life with our A4 Matt Photo Paper (Sticker). Whether you’re crafting, decorating, or organizing, this versatile paper is sure to inspire endless possibilities.

Description
Introducing our A4 Iron-On Inkjet Transfer Paper for Dark Color Cotton Material – the ultimate solution for creating vibrant, personalized designs on dark fabrics! Each pack contains premium-quality transfer paper specially formulated to produce vivid, long-lasting results.
 Designed for ease of use and durability, our iron-on transfer paper allows you to effortlessly print your favorite designs, photos, or text onto dark-colored cotton garments and fabrics using an inkjet printer. Simply print, trim, and iron on for professional-quality results that stand the test of time.
Perfect for a variety of applications, including:
Custom Apparel: Create one-of-a-kind T-shirts, hoodies, tote bags, and more with personalized designs that reflect your unique style.
Gifts and Keepsakes: Make meaningful gifts for friends and family by transferring cherished photos or heartfelt messages onto fabric.
Team Uniforms and Spirit Wear: Show your team pride with custom jerseys, uniforms, and fan gear that feature your team’s logo or mascot.
Event Merchandise: Generate buzz for your event or fundraiser with branded merchandise like shirts, hats, and bandanas featuring your event’s logo or slogan.
DIY Projects: Get creative with home decor projects like throw pillows, canvas wall art, and fabric banners, adding a personalized touch to any space.
With its A4 size, our iron-on transfer paper provides ample space for large, detailed designs or multiple smaller transfers on a single sheet. Plus, the advanced transfer technology ensures that your designs adhere smoothly to the fabric, resulting in a soft, flexible finish that won’t crack or peel.
Transform your dark-colored cotton fabrics into works of art with our A4 Iron-On Inkjet Transfer Paper. Whether you’re expressing your creativity, promoting your brand, or commemorating a special occasion, our transfer paper makes it easy to turn your ideas into reality.
